response.overview: The series is set in North Chennai's Vaali Nagar where some work as henchmen under different organised crime networks and are called 'labels'. Meanwhile, Prabha (Jai), a lawyer who hails from the same area, is working hard to remove the stereotypes and improve his neighbourhood.
response.tagline: The protagonist struggle to reach his desired identity and overcoming the identity society has labelled him with.
response.title: Label
